Term(s) of Office: 1892 - 1894

The Right Honourable Sir John Thompson __ "John Thompson's support for women's rights is only one aspect of the passion for fairness and justice that informed not just his ideals, but his actions as well. That the reputation of Canada's fourth prime minister has since sunk into obscurity is due to the unfortunate brevity of his term of office."
